OL,3,CWar within a war: Yemini children
OL,4,Cstruggle for water in city under siege
OL,6,FYemini children clutch at empty water
OL,7,Fbottles tasked with stopping their
OL,8,Ffamilies from dying of thirst, ITV
OL,9,FNews Global Security Editor Rohit
OL,10,FKachroo reports from Taizz, Yemen
OL,12,FYoung boys wearing football shirts
OL,13,Fmake friends and share jokes while
OL,14,Fthey wait.
OL,16,FA girl in a ballerina dress smiles as
OL,17,Fshe counts the number of footsteps
OL,18,Ffrom one side of the pavement to the
OL,19,Fother.
