OL,6,FHe has tried to escape the besieged
OL,7,Fcity before but was refused by Houthi
OL,8,Fsoldiers.
OL,10,F"They saw that I was from a government-
OL,11,Fcontrolled area, and they said 'You
OL,12,Fare from ISIS'. It was their first
OL,13,Fword: 'You are from ISIS!'"
OL,15,FNow, trapped in Taizz, he relies on
OL,16,Fthese occasional deliveries from a
OL,17,Ftruck carrying huge containers of
OL,18,Fwater.
