OL,6,FShe is eight years old and weighs only
OL,7,Fseven kilograms ` too weak to scream
OL,8,Fand even to move.
OL,10,FThe surgeon names some of the
OL,11,Fconditions she is now suffering from `
OL,12,Fa list so long he cannot recall them
OL,13,Fall. "Malnutrition, diarrhoea, heart
OL,14,Ffailure".
OL,16,FHe rates her chances of survival at no
OL,17,Fmore than 10%.
