OL,6,F"But there is no one in the village
OL,7,Fwho can speak up on behalf of all of
OL,8,Fus to say we don't have water."
OL,10,FIt is the men behind the war in Yemen
OL,11,F` and, specifically, the siege of
OL,12,FTaizz ` who have prevented water from
OL,13,Fflowing to those who need it.
OL,15,FWe are here to report on the campaign
OL,16,Fby Houthis against commercial shipping
OL,17,Fin and around the Red Sea which has
OL,18,Fused an array of sophisticated
OL,19,Fballistic missiles and so-called
OL,20,F'kamikaze' drones.
