OL,3,CWar within a war: Yemini children
OL,4,Cstruggle for water in city under siege
OL,6,FBut as we meet the malnourished
OL,7,Fchildren of the city, it is obvious
OL,8,Fthat there is a greater weapon in the
OL,9,FHouthi arsenal which deserves our
OL,10,Fattention, aimed at Yemeni people
OL,11,Frather than commercial ships.
OL,13,FThe group has blocked water flowing
OL,14,Finto the government-controlled city,
OL,15,Fforcing some people to collect
OL,16,Frainwater.
OL,18,FAccording to Human Rights Watch, both
OL,19,FHouthi and Yemeni forces have violated
OL,20,Fthe rights of Taizz residents to water.
