OL,6,FIt claims the Houthis have blocked
OL,7,Fwater flowing into the city from the
OL,8,Ftwo basins under its control and have
OL,9,Fprevented some water trucks from
OL,10,Faccessing government-controlled areas.
OL,12,FHRW also says military forces
OL,13,Faffiliated with the Yemeni government
OL,14,Ftook control of some wells and sold
OL,15,Fsupplies to residents for profit.
