OL,3,CWar within a war: Yemini children
OL,4,Cstruggle for water in city under siege
OL,6,FWe find a hillside to get a view
OL,7,Facross the city. From there, the
OL,8,Ffrontline is visible - a dark, green
OL,9,Fbank close to the mountains which
OL,10,Flooks like it has been drawn with a
OL,11,Fgiant marker pen from left to right
OL,12,Facross the landscape.
OL,14,FBeyond it, heading into the hills is
OL,15,Fthe territory controlled by the
OL,16,FHouthis, who are backed by Iran. On
OL,17,Fthis side, the Yemeni government is in
OL,18,Fcharge, which has the support of Saudi
OL,19,FArabia and the United States.
